{"content": "<h2>The Artist: Vinnie Hager</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Vinne Hager has refined his visual language into a series of symbols derived from a master set of 100 diary drawings made over a period of a decade. In these drawings lay the clues to a newfound strength to grow through art. Unlike the outward protest symbols present of Keith Haring's work, Hagers symbols to date are more introspective. The 'envelope' top left in 'Smudge Smudge' from 2020,  the 'crying eye' in 'Vanity Plate Party Nachoes' from 2019, the 'Smiley Balloon' from 'Zoom Fatigue' and the structured doodling in 'Friday To Do List' are the foundations for future greatness.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"522\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/vinne-hager-100-1024x714.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/vinne-hager-100-1024x714.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/vinne-hager-100-300x209.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/vinne-hager-100-768x535.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/vinne-hager-100-1536x1071.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/vinne-hager-100-1320x920.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/vinne-hager-100-600x418.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/vinne-hager-100.png 1896w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Original 100 from Diary by Vinnie Hager</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t<p>42 of the 100 hand drawings were minted randomly during the 24 hours the mint window stayed open. These were eligible to have the original 1/1 drawing claimed and sent to the collectoor.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: Diary by Vinnie Hager</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Diary expands on the Original 100 hand drawings by generating a large 1/1/x format collection minted 3,100 times. Each mint was a potential moment to win one of the Original 100 hand drawings as well as 12 beautiful visual diary entries of their own. The 12 'Entry' traits decided the composition and the 30 'Palette' traits directed the applied colors, with a further 'Color' trait increasing or reducing the range of colors between two and seven.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"611\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Hemisphere-palette-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-1024x836.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Hemisphere-palette-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-1024x836.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Hemisphere-palette-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-300x245.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Hemisphere-palette-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-768x627.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Hemisphere-palette-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-1536x1254.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Hemisphere-palette-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-1320x1078.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Hemisphere-palette-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-600x490.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Hemisphere-palette-Vinnie-Hager-Diary.png 1908w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Hemisphere palette in Diary collection by Vinnie Hager</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/To-Do-Lists-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-1024x656.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/To-Do-Lists-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-1024x656.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/To-Do-Lists-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-300x192.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/To-Do-Lists-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-768x492.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/To-Do-Lists-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-1536x985.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/To-Do-Lists-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-1320x846.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/To-Do-Lists-Vinnie-Hager-Diary-600x385.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/To-Do-Lists-Vinnie-Hager-Diary.png 2034w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>'To Do Lists' Entries trait in the Diary collection</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: Hey NVM Wait</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Hey NVM Wait is the 1/1 artwork that MintFace was lucky enough to mint straight out of the gate. The year of the diary entry is shown in the bottom right as 2021. Words written include 'Coinbase' and 'Chainlink' indicating that Hager was fully into crypto already and introducing new crypto related symbolism into his visual language. I am yet to discover what the title 'Hey NVM Wait' means. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Diary-by-Vinnie-Hager-11-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Diary-by-Vinnie-Hager-11-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Diary-by-Vinnie-Hager-11-300x225.jpg 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Diary-by-Vinnie-Hager-11-768x576.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Diary-by-Vinnie-Hager-11-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Diary-by-Vinnie-Hager-11-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Diary-by-Vinnie-Hager-11-400x300.jpg 400w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Diary-by-Vinnie-Hager-11-1320x990.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Diary-by-Vinnie-Hager-11-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>'Hey NVM Wait' 1/1 by Vinnie Hager</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t<p>Hager is applying his aesthetic surface that will have it including everything from fast flowing merch and slow setting concrete walls. Expect to see these symbols at every cryptoart festival and exhibition for the foreseeable future.</p>"}